      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This car is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is for parts or as a major restoration project. The engine is currently non-functional, and there is significant rust damage along the undercarriage and wheel wells. The interior has seen better days, with torn upholstery and a cracked dashboard, while the exterior paint is heavily faded with multiple dents. It will need to be towed away, as it is not currently roadworthy.",
